# Intentional — the following checks are turned off:
# SC2086: $extra intentionally unquoted (holds multiple flags; word splitting needed)
# SC2254: $OWNER_PAT in `case` is an intentional glob (owner-pattern allowlist), not a literal match
# SC2004: $/${} inside $(( )) is a deliberate readability choice (harmless style nit)
# SC1090/SC1091: resources.conf is sourced dynamically (path resolved at runtime)
disable=SC2086,SC2254,SC2004,SC1090,SC1091
